{
  "stem": "13483.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All you could write, say, whether you were fit and well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, and it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] some-- some letters were terribly censored.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember I once wrote a letter to my wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After I came back from the army, I got demobilized from the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She showed me this letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About three quarters of it was cut out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I can't remember if I'd ever mentioned anything that you could call security reasons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was censored, very heavily censored.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which makes sense, in any case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember they said that we were going into one of the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think at the time they said, we're going to a place called Bergen-Belsen, which we didn't attach the Belsen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we heard [INAUDIBLE] again, was Bergen on the Hill, or Belsen, or Bergen on the Hill, or Belsen on the Hill.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we had heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that it was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did hear that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- well, all the things that you could hear about a concentration camp, I suppose we heard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you'd have to go ahead and do it, irrespective of the circumstances or what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I suppose as a Jewish soldier, I had great feelings of qualm and uneasiness.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I thought I-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I can't actually explain-- describe my feelings, not at the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's only when I actually got into the camp, that after, I felt-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] disbelief.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What I saw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had the military prepared you for what you might see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they told us it was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us it was notorious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said probably what you'll see may shock you.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
